                            <comment id="14648083" author="lehmi" created="Thu, 30 Jul 2015 18:28:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;IMHO there are two possible solutions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;close all streams after merging as proposed on SO&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;collect all FileInputStreams created within addSource and close them after merging&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="14648091" author="tilman" created="Thu, 30 Jul 2015 18:33:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The 2nd would be more logical, i.e. &quot;you close what you open&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
